        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroformylation reaction",
        "description": "在30-80°C和10-40 bar CO/H₂条件下，使用2.6 wt% Rh/Al-SBA-15催化剂，在THF或甲苯溶剂中对苯乙烯进行氢甲酰化反应，生成2-苯基丙醛和3-苯基丙醛",
        "text_snippet": "Hydroformylation of styrene under a CO/H₂ atmosphere was first studied at 30–80 °C and 10–40 bar over 2.6 wt% Rh/Al-SBA-15 in tetrahydrofuran (THF) or toluene solvents... Toluene favoured higher (98%) conversion and selectivity (90%) to 2-phenylpropanal (A) and 3-phenylpropanal (B)",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "羟烷基化-烷基化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroxyalkylation-alkylation (HAA) reaction",
        "description": "在65°C条件下，使用Al-SBA-15固体酸催化剂，将苯甲醛与2-甲基呋喃进行羟烷基化-烷基化反应，生成2-甲基-5-[(5-甲基呋喃-2-基)-苯甲基]呋喃",
        "text_snippet": "Hydroxyalkylation–alkylation of benzaldehyde with 2-MF was negligible without a solid acid present or at 50 °C over Al-SBA-15... 65% benzaldehyde conversion and a near quantitative yield (>99% selectivity) of the 2-methyl-5-[(5-methylfuran-2-yl)-phenylmethyl]furan... HAA product was obtained at 65 °C after 1.5 h reaction",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
